                                <h3 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1">What is a GCC and how can MOAR Advisory help?</button></h3>
                                <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#moarFAQ"><div class="accordion-body">A Global Capability Center (GCC) is a strategic offshore unit that drives innovation, technology, and business processes. MOAR Advisory helps organizations establish, operate, and scale GCCs with end-to-end advisory covering setup, talent, technology, and compliance.</div></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="accordion-item">
