                                <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#moarFAQ"><div class="accordion-body">We serve retail, manufacturing, financial services, healthcare, aviation, and technology sectors — bringing deep domain expertise to each engagement.</div></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="accordion-item">
                                <h3 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">How does MOAR Advisory differ from traditional consulting firms?</button></h3>
                                <div id="faq3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#moarFAQ"><div class="accordion-body">We are practitioners, not consultants. Our team embeds with yours and drives hands-on execution — not just recommendations. We combine advisory expertise with operational delivery for measurable outcomes.</div></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="accordion-item">
                                <h3 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq4">How does MOAR Advisory offer advisory &amp; GCC integrated services?</button></h3>
                                <div id="faq4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#moarFAQ"><div class="accordion-body">We provide a full spectrum of services from feasibility studies and location advisory through to company setup, talent acquisition, employer branding, and technology transformation — all integrated under one advisory partnership.</div></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
